    .ui.container
      h2.ui.header.title-m
        | Background Story
      p
        | We designed this plugin extension as a 
        i
          | humanized ui
        |  element for social networking sites that need to faciliate relations between people. Research shows that people are extremely sensitvie to photos of others, so we needed to revamp the traditional ui elements to make them more intuitive and human.
      p
        | You can use these plugin extensions for modelling multiple 
        code.highlighter-rouge
          | one-to-many
        |  or single 
        code.highlighter-rouge
          | one-to-one
        |  relations between people.
      h2.ui.header.title-m
        | Multiple Select
      p
        | This example shows the 
        code.highlighter-rouge
          | multiple select
        |  scenario. 
      select.my-select[multiple="multiple"]
        option[data-img-src="img/adnan.png"]
          | Adnan Sagar
        option[selected="selected" data-img-src="img/rena.png"]
          | Rena Cugelman
        option[selected="selected" data-img-src="img/tavis.png"]
          | Tavis Lochhead
        option[data-img-src="img/brian.png"]
          | Brain Cugelman
      code.xml.cm-s-mdn-like
        select[multiple="multiple"]
          option[data-img-src="img/adnan.png"]
            | Adnan Sagar
          option[data-img-src="img/rena.png" selected="selected"]
            | Rena Cugelman
          option[data-img-src="img/tavis.png" selected="selected"]
            | Tavis Lochhead
          option[data-img-src="img/brian.png"]
            | Brain Cugelman
      p
        | As shown above, use 
        code.highlighter-rouge
          | data-img-src
        |  attribute to attache images. Finally, enable 
        i
          | Image Select
        |  by invoking the 
        code.highlighter-rouge
          | chosen
        |  method on the select element.
      .javascript.cm-s-mdn-like
        |  $(".my-select").chosen({ width:"100%", }); 
      .ui.warning.message
        .header
          |  Info 
        |  For more details check 
        a[href="http://harvesthq.github.io/chosen/"]
          | Chosen documentation
        | . 
      h2.ui.header.title-m
        | Single Select
      p
        | For single select, remove the 
        code.highlighter-rouge
          | multiple
        |  attribute. 
      select.my-select
        option
          | Please select, ...
        option[data-img-src="img/adnan.png"]
